==English==

===Etymology===
From post-Classical {{etyl|la|en}}; either from {{term|rectilīneāris|lang=la}} or from {{term|rectilīneus|lang=la}} (whence {{term|rectiline|lang=en}}) + {{term|-ar|lang=en}}, in both cases ultimately deriving from {{term|rectus||straight|lang=la}} + {{term|līnea||line|lang=la}}.

